<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Helter-skelter" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Helter-skelter,</orth> an expression denoting the utmost haste: <cit><quote>and h. have I rode to thee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.3.98" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 3, 98</bibl></cit> (Pistol's words).
